fce50_name_file_1280x720_2000_v3_1_.jpg?auth=abbce8b806a390760d0cc6bb3076d69372cb93af46e1a966b8850e6dfbe5dceb&width=800&height=450&smart=true", "https://gray-wfie-prod.gtv-cdn.com/resizer/v2/EGXWELUN5ZDV5NMPF66IMB6IYQ.jpg?auth=347beeb53c5916baddb2b855e346386ccbbe72f2f637ce453e0fc0541f1a0eb0&width=800&height=450&smart=true", "https://gray-wfie-prod.gtv-cdn.com/resizer/v2/77U2UEIFKRDH3OBCM23VIKB5LY.jpg?auth=84064de319108c5ea26da752f13b8255c0a2518162ae2ad50e1f7ab1d0cc78aa&width=800&height=450&smart=true", "https://gray-wfie-prod.gtv-cdn.com/resizer/v2/YEPQLZYNIRDPFBRLQPJVJGWUME.jpg?auth=92bed3f11fdd880750f260154b22dce8a71c8aeabd7128a656a24d422ab37521&width=800&height=450&smart=true", "https://gray-wfie-prod.gtv-cdn.com/resizer/v2/LI62OF5IKVFIFHMJHDCTXU4E7M.jpg?auth=dec58616a5caee5df4c642ae063d73f1f622a4310711ba1bc33f09e7e4000c5f&width=800&height=450&smart=true", "https://gray-wfie-prod.gtv-cdn.com/resizer/v2/QBGUGTC7M5DFLKZGBAKRVTTM2E.jpg?auth=54270cfd7adcac3b68e05dc2fed21318f91189d6e6ea5c88f342b0394107238e&width=800&height=450&smart=true", "https://gray-wfie-prod.gtv-cdn.com/resizer/v2/7YBAJUVUTFAGBL257GJBCCT744.jpeg?auth=1f5c99ed5f99c91b939a2d94f43e4c557d088c65c5cf951ccc9bb5e32750de22&width=800&height=450&smart=true"], "publication-date": "2024-08-27", "text": "EVANSVILLE, Ind. (WFIE) - The Evansville Police Department and the Vanderburgh County Sheriff’s Office partnered with Dunkin Donuts to help raise money for Special Olympics of Indiana.\n\nEarlier this month, the “Cop on a Rooftop” event took place, where officers stood on the rooftop of Dunkin Donuts.\n\nPolice say our area raised just shy of $1,300 dollars, which put them 4th out of 14 agencies who took part in the fundraiser.\n\nOfficers say Dunkin’ Donuts staff even donated their tips that day to boost their numbers.\n\nCopyright 2024 WFIE. All rights reserved.", "title": "‘Cops on a Roof’ raises over $1,000 for Special Olympics of Indiana", "top-image": "https://gray-wfie-prod.gtv-cdn.com/resizer/v2/KHZMIRIZKVEIFOKHDJV33ZQKPM.png?auth=8c2016954acbd25ea8cb256030e395833be0da29450bb16c365ce7e7faba84c9&width=800&height=450&smart=true", "domain": "www.14news.com", "lang": "en", "author": "", "description": "Officers stood on the rooftop of Dunkin Donuts for a good cause.", "keywords": ""}